"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-5-21-australian-breaker-raygun-swaps-lecture-theatre-for-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Breaking is a new sport at the Paris Olympics with athletes from different backgrounds and ages vying to take part.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  The athletes battling for breaking gold at the Olympics will bring an array of tricks to Paris but Australia's Dr\\u00a0Rachael\\u00a0Gunn\\u00a0may be the only one armed with a PhD in the sport's culture.\", \"from\": 117, \"to\": 317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999964012314376, \"rank\": 3.5987813315696312e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 229, \"end\": 238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9998193935048064, \"rank\": 0.00012986415324194264, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"score\": 0.9999999998440217, \"rank\": 1.5576406001833255e-10, \"text\": \"Rachael\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rachael_Ray\"}, {\"begin\": 252, \"end\": 256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old known as \\\"Raygun\\\", a portmanteau of her name, completed a thesis in 2017 on the intersection of gender in Sydney's breaking scene while training to become one of the nation's top dancers.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999529545687, \"rank\": 4.500034102147892e-08, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Macquarie University lecturer will soon take time out from academia to compete at the Place de la Concorde, where breaking will make its Olympic debut some 50 years after emerging from the streets of the Bronx.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 528, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9851037212467226e-22, \"text\": \"Macquarie University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Macquarie_University\"}, {\"begin\": 614, \"end\": 634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"score\": 0.9999999999126885, \"rank\": 8.752514617637167e-11, \"text\": \"Place de la Concorde\", \"types\": [\"Q34442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Place_de_la_Concorde\"}, {\"begin\": 732, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"score\": 0.9999999881670193, \"rank\": 8.726396071571848e-09, \"text\": \"Bronx\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Bronx\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A university faculty office may seem an unlikely habitat for a breaking champion, and\\u00a0Gunn\\u00a0laughs when confirming she is unaware of any other academics moonlighting in the sport.\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People certainly think it's cool and interesting, but it's also really different to the classic academic path,\\\" she told Reuters in an interview.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1042, \"end\": 1049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999981600922, \"rank\": 1.8185591875779617e-09, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So you do get a few different reactions depending on which department or faculty people are from.\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1166, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But by and large, the response has been really positive.\\\"\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1224, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn did not take up breaking until her mid-20s and stands out among the teenagers qualified to date, who include Lithuanian world champion Dominika Banevic, a 16-year-old who competes as \\\"B-girl Nicka\\\".\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1226, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuanian_language\", \"score\": 0.965567589616364, \"rank\": 0.012757415644821753, \"text\": \"Lithuanian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lithuanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australia's male qualifier Jeff \\\"J-Attack\\\" Dunne is also 16.\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet Gunn is far from an anomaly, with American rival Sunny Choi also set to fly the flag for mid-30s breakers at Paris after giving up a corporate career.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999984843291981, \"rank\": 8.36420421374478e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1552, \"end\": 1556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ada_Choi\", \"score\": 0.9999996906995444, \"rank\": 3.0930043825583185e-07, \"text\": \"Choi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ada_Choi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ada_Choi\"}, {\"begin\": 1606, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999964012314376, \"rank\": 3.5987813315696312e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Younger bodies have it easier learning and perfecting \\\"power moves\\\", the more acrobatic elements of breaking that often demand speed, strength and momentum,\\u00a0Gunn\\u00a0concedes.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1820, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1806, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, she is still trying out - and nailing - new elements with the help of her husband and coach Samuel Free, a competitive breaker under the name \\\"Sammy The Free\\\".\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a different experience.\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 2021, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I obviously spend more time warming up, more time in recovery and just make sure I look after my body,\\\" said\\u00a0Gunn.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not think a 20-year-old needs to worry as much about those things.\\\"\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Two gold medals are up for grabs in the breaking competition in Paris, one each for the best male and female dancer, .\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2331, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2277, \"end\": 2282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999964012314376, \"rank\": 3.5987813315696312e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dancers, who call themselves \\\"B-boys\\\" and \\\"B-girls\\\", compete in one-on-one battles in three, minute-long \\\"throw downs\\\", with the music chosen by a DJ and performances scored by a panel of judges.\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking was popular at the Youth Olympics in Buenos Aires in 2018 and drew enthusiastic crowds at its Asian Games debut in China last year.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2576, \"end\": 2588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"score\": 0.9999999801043489, \"rank\": 1.9522199098059663e-08, \"text\": \"Buenos Aires\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Buenos_Aires\"}, {\"begin\": 2654, \"end\": 2659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9875440029673338, \"rank\": 0.006898627919050799, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, its addition to the Olympic programme has had its detractors, who have dismissed it as a desperate ploy by the International Olympic Committee to attract a younger audience.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2792, \"end\": 2823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some dancers are also sceptical about how breaking's underground roots and street culture fit the commercialised Olympic movement.\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The critics may be happy that Los Angeles Olympic organisers declined to retain breaking for the 2028 Games.\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999997598934, \"rank\": 2.3094627572547027e-10, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though Raygun can see both sides of the debate, she raves about a highly accessible sport which has become a lot more inclusive and respectful of women since she penned her thesis.\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3278, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3105, \"end\": 3111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.272245290504178e-26, \"text\": \"Raygun\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Raygun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics may also help put breaking on the map in Australia, where there are limited money-making opportunities compared with markets in East Asia and Europe.\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3334, \"end\": 3343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9998193935048064, \"rank\": 0.00012986415324194264, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Breaking has such a positive force and impact on people's lives that do it,\\\" said\\u00a0Gunn.\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3527, \"end\": 3531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9378915979022769, \"rank\": 0.05962529370360896, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trey_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They get fit, they get a creative outlet and become part of this community.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The platform that the Olympics gives us to inspire new generations of people is positive.\\\"\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3701, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 3721, \"to\": 3747, \"entities\": []}]}"